</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="padding: 0px; padding-top: 2px; text-align:center; font-size:100%;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Bensteindol.jpg" class="image" title="Bensteindol.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Bensteindol.jpg/310px-Bensteindol.jpg" width="310" height="224" border="0" /></a><br />
